{"word":"ἐμβιβάζω","slug":"ἐμβιβάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐμβιβάζω</b></el> <el>(attic <a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-βιβῶ</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>Causal of <a href='S:ἐμβαίνω'><el>ἐμβαίνω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to set in</i> or <i>on</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>:— <i>to put on board ship, cause to embark</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to lead</i> to a thing, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}